## Limitations
This report is limited by the availability of sources and the potential bias in retrospective analyses. The data is primarily from Western perspectives, which may not fully capture the global implications of 9/11. Additionally, the evolving nature of security policies and cultural perceptions means that the impact of 9/11 continues to develop, potentially altering future interpretations of its legacy.

